   20395             : /**********************************************************************
   20396             :  *                     MITABLoadCoordSysTable()
   20397             :  *
   20398             :  * Load a Coordsys bounds lookup table from an external file.
   20399             :  * The entries from that table will be looked up in priority BEFORE the
   20400             :  * entries from gasBoundsList[] defined above.
   20401             :  *
   20402             :  * This allows users to override the default bounds for existing
   20403             :  * projections, and to define bounds for new projections not listed in
   20404             :  * the table above.
   20405             :  *
   20406             :  * The format of the file is a simple text file with one CoordSys string
   20407             :  * per line.  The CoordSys lines should follow the MIF specs, and MUST
   20408             :  * include the optional Bounds definition at the end of the line.
   20409             :  *
   20410             :  * e.g.
   20411             :  *  CoordSys Earth Projection 8, 24, "m", -63, 0, 0.9996, 500000, 0 Bounds \
   20412             :  *  (-7746230.6469039, -9998287.383889269) (8746230.6469039, 9998287.383889269)
   20413             :  *
   20414             :  * Returns 0 on success, -1 on error.
   20415             :  **********************************************************************/

   20425             :     {

   20427           6 :         int numEntries = 100;
   20428             :

   20436             :
